  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and efficacy of QGE031 versus placebo in patients with bullous
      pemphigoid.  Efficacy will be assessed as a reduction of disease activity.  How QGE031 is
      broken down by the body and the impact it has on different blood and tissue markers will
      also be explored.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
